{{Youmay|the SE2 service droid|the [[SE-2-4 servant droid]] or the canon [[SE-2 worker droid]]}}
The '''SE2 service droid''' was a [[Droid/Legends|droid]] model that was working in the Imperial Archives on [[Bastion/Legends|Bastion]] when [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] and [[Lando Calrissian/Legends|Lando Calrissian]] went there to look for a copy of the [[Caamas Document]] to end a dispute on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]].

==Appearances==
